## ðŸ§© Code Snippet:

### ðŸ”¹ 3423. Maximum Difference Between Adjacent Elements in a Circular Array
```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    int maxAdjacentDistance(vector<int>& nums) {
        int n = nums.size();
        int mDif = abs(nums[0] - nums[n - 1]);
        for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {
            mDif = max(mDif, abs(nums[i] - nums[i + 1]));
        }
        return mDif;
    }
};
```
